period. He is further concerned with the number and varying nature of the communications 
sent, particularly those that address threats against journalists and human rights defenders. 
The Special Rapporteur calls on the Government to take all necessary measures to create a 
safe and enabling environment for human rights defenders and journalists to carry out their 
legitimate activities without the fear of being killed. 
