</b></p>
<p>81. The Special Rapporteur thanks the Government of Uganda for its response. The 
Special welcomes the information that investigations are being carried out into the conduct 
of police officers who acted outside the scope of their powers and that one matter is before 
the court. He would appreciate receiving information on the outcome of these investigations 
and judicial proceedings.  
</p>
